# App routes (app/)

## Route tree

- `_layout.tsx` — Root layout (QueryClient, AuthContext, DataSourceProvider)
- `(tabs)/` — Tab group
  - `_layout.tsx` — Tab layout
  - `index.tsx` — Home
  - `data.tsx` — Data tab
  - `habits/` — Habits feature
  - `quick-wins/` — Quick Wins (iOS only; shows dated Reminders for selected day)
    - `index.tsx` — Quick Wins list
    - `_layout.tsx` — Habits layout
    - `index.tsx` — Habits list
    - `[habitId].tsx` — Habit detail (dynamic)
- `auth/` — Authentication routes
- `+not-found.tsx` — 404
- `global.css` — Global NativeWind styles

## Routing

- File-based routing with Expo Router. Grouped routes use `(tabs)`; dynamic segment is `[habitId].tsx`.
- Each segment can have its own `_layout.tsx` for nested layouts.
- Use `app/global.css` for global styles; avoid page-level StyleSheet or style objects.

## Auth

- Auth UI routes live under `auth/`. Auth state is provided by `AuthContext` (from `db/`); use it for session and login overlay flows.
